Project refactor TODO - history preparers

Goal: extract duplicated logic between file-mode and repo-mode history preparers
into small, testable helper methods. For each helper:
- implement helper in the indicated class
- update one `_prep` function to use it
- run `scripts/test_prep_backends.py ../test-repo` and `scripts/check_axioms.py`
- when green, update the corresponding other preparer to use it and test again

Workflow: go slowly, one helper at a time. Mark items as done as tests pass.

- [ ] 1. Add `AppBase._run_git_lines(repo_root: str, args: list[str], label: str) -> list[str]`
      - implemented: `AppBase._run_git_lines(cmd: list[str], label: str|None) -> list[str]`
      - replaced raw `subprocess` calls in one `_prep..._for_git` site and updated tests

- [ ] 2. Add `AppBase._canonical_relpath(path: str, repo_root: str) -> str`
      - implemented: `AppBase._canonical_relpath(path: str, repo_root: str) -> str` (normalizes to realpath)

- [x] 3. Add `AppBase._compute_pseudo_timestamps(repo_root: str, mods: list[str], single_path: str) -> (mods_ts, staged_ts)`
      - completed: computes latest mtime for `mods` or for a single path, and index mtime

 - [x] 4. Add `AppBase._format_pseudo_summary(pseudo_entries: list[tuple[str,str]])`
       - implemented: central helper appended pseudo-summary rows and attached metadata; repo- and file-mode preparers now use it

- [ ] 5. Add `AppBase._parse_git_log_lines(lines: list[str]) -> list[tuple[datetime,str,str]]`
      - centralize robust parsing of git log output

- [x] 6. Add `HistoryListBase._format_commit_row(dt: datetime, hash: str, msg: str) -> str`
      - implemented: centralized commit row formatting used by history preparers

- [ ] 7. Add `AppBase._append_file_row(display: str, full_path: str, is_dir: bool=False, status: str|None=None)`
