- [ ] 9. Replace duplicated `pygit2 vs git` parity test scaffolding with `AppBase._compare_backends`

- [ ] 10. Run full regression: `scripts/test_prep_backends.py ../test-repo` and then `scripts/check_axioms.py`.

Notes:
- Each TODO item should be completed, tested, and marked checked before moving to the next.
